ebrity Family Feud]]''\n| Herself\n| 1 episode\n|-\n| 2017\n| ''[[Great News]]''\n| Angie Deltaliano\n| 4 episodes\n|-\n| 2018&ndash;19\n| ''[[The Cool Kids (TV series)|The Cool Kids]]''\n| Margaret\n| Starring role\n|}\n\n==Discography==\n\n===Albums===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\"| Year\n! rowspan=\"2\"| Album\n! colspan=\"2\"| Chart positions<ref name=\"Billboard\">{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/music/vicki-lawrence/chart-history|title=Vicki Lawrence Chart History|work=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]|accessdate=April 16, 2020}}</ref>\n! rowspan=\"2\"| Catalog #\n|-\n! style=\"width:50px;\"| <small>[[Billboard 200|US]]</small>\n! style=\"width:50px;\"| <small>[[Canadian Albums Chart|CAN]]</small>\n|-\n| 1973\n| ''[[The Night the Lights Went Out in Georgia (Vicki Lawrence album)|The Night the Lights Went Out in Georgia]]''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 51\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 31\n| Bell 1120\n|-\n| 1974\n| ''Ships in the Night''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| \u2014\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| \u2014\n| SOSL10106\n|-\n| 1979\n| ''Newborn Woman''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| \u2014\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| \u2014\n| WindMill L26\n|}\n\n===Singles===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\"| Year\n! rowspan=\"2\"| Song\n! colspan=\"8\"| Chart positions<ref name=\"Billboard\"/><ref>{{cite book|last=Kent|first=David|authorlink=David Kent (historian)|title=Australian Chart Book 1970\u20131992|publisher=Australian Chart Book|location=St. Ives, N.S.W.|year=1993|edition=Illustrated|isbn=0-646-11917-6}}</ref>\n! rowspan=\"2\"| Album\n|- style=\"font-size:smaller;\"\n! style=\"width:35px;\"| [[Billboard Hot 100|US]]\n! style=\"width:35px;\"| [[Adult Contemporary (chart)|US AC]]\n! style=\"width:35px;\"| [[Hot Country Songs|US Country]]\n! style=\"width:35px;\"| CAN\n! style=\"width:35px;\"| CAN AC\n! style=\"width:35px;\"| CAN Country\n! style=\"width:35px;\"| [[Kent Music Report|